
# General
- for GUI front, field name should be display with space instead of _
- the json-schemat keyword "default": null should be respected. For those case, the GUI should not generate empty field (as \[] or "")Note that for "Handling_restrictions" and "Suitable_SC_IDs", is set to "default": [].
- example should pre fill field until user clic on it


## Assignement
For each handling, if any of the Handling_restrictions set match, the Suitable_SCs list will be assigned to the handling. By default, the first SC in the list will be use. But if resources are used for another handling, the next SC can be use (depending of PAS_builder settings).
